We have immediate move-in availability on a 2 bedroom 2 baths 900 ft² newly renovated duplex with fresh paint, upgraded kitchen, and bath.

Thoughtfully designed with comfort in mind, our floor plans feature a wide array of stylishly efficient amenities including a breakfast bar, all-electric kitchen, refrigerator, pantry, tile flooring, ceiling fans, mini blinds, central air conditioning and heating, washer and dryer connections, private backyard and more.
We bring you to comfort living at its best.
